 decide you want to complete only the Basic Course.</div><div><br><b>Subtitles for all video lectures available in</b>: Portuguese (provided by <a href="http://www.fundacaolemann.org.br/" target="_blank">The Lemann Foundation</a>), English<br></div>', 'https://www.coursera.org/course/maththink', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0xCRl54AjX0', '2013-03-04', 10, 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/coursera/topics/maththink/large-icon.png', 'Mathematics', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'yes', ' Stanford University', '2014-05-18 22:40:40'),
